import React from 'react'
import NavigationButton from './navigation-button'
import {
    Twitter,
    HomeFill,
    Basket,
    Notification,
    Profile,
    SettingsFill,
} from './icon'
import styles from './navigation.module.css'
import TextTitle from './text-title'

function Navigation({ selectedKey }) {
    return (
        <nav className={styles.nav}>
            <NavigationButton selected={selectedKey === 'home'}>
                <HomeFill />
                <TextTitle>Ana Sayfa</TextTitle>
            </NavigationButton>

            <NavigationButton selected={selectedKey === 'basket'}>
                <Basket />
                <TextTitle>Sipari≈ülerim</TextTitle>
            </NavigationButton>

            <NavigationButton selected={selectedKey === 'notification'}>
                <Notification />
                <TextTitle>Bildirimler</TextTitle>
            </NavigationButton>

            <NavigationButton selected={selectedKey === 'profile'}>
                <Profile />
                <TextTitle>Profil</TextTitle>
            </NavigationButton>

            <NavigationButton selected={selectedKey === 'settings'}>
                <SettingsFill />
                <TextTitle>Ayarlar</TextTitle>
            </NavigationButton>
        </nav>
    )
}
export default Navigation
